WorldManager - Class in cz.cuni.mff.kocur.world
This class manages the world World update will take these steps: First the client will use a POST message to send some data The data will be in JSON and they will contain id of the bot that issued the update Manager should then take the data and parse the to objects that correspond to the World objects Then we will update the world information by rewriting the objects in the world Manager should allow bots to query for informations that are close to them.
